                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8734" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0257</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2522 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">到底谁是实际控制人？——中炬高新控制权争夺战</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Who is the Actual Controller?——The Control Rights Battle in JonjeE HI-TECH</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵宇恒，闻人皓洋，黄梦曦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中炬高新技术实业（集团）股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司治理；实际控制人；控制权争夺；国资管控；国企改革；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate Governance； Actual Controller；Control Rights Battle；State-owned Assets Management；State-owned Enterprise Reform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新《公司法》的出台和新一轮国企改革方案的推进，为完善中国特色现代企业制度注入了新动力。在此背景下，企业应当重塑治理机制，强化内控与合规管理，并加强风险防控；同时，国有股东应当充分发挥在公司治理中的作用，关注投资企业的控制权归属，特别是实际控制人行为是否符合公司利益等问题。基于此，本案例围绕“实际控制人”这一核心知识点，再现宝能系和火炬系争夺中炬高新控制权的全过程。一方面旨在寻求控制权争夺背后的原因，分析中炬高新存在的公司治理问题；另一方面，通过观察国有股东火炬集团对中炬高新控制权需求的转变，理解国企改革对国资管控提出的新要求。最终，深入思考企业应如何重塑公司治理机制，以保障内部控制和风险管理的有效性，确保企业稳定经营。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The enactment of the new Company Law and the advancement of the new round of state-owned enterprise reform have injected new impetus into the perfecting of the modern enterprise system with Chinese characteristics. Under this background, enterprises should reshape their governance mechanisms, strengthen internal control and compliance management, and enhance risk prevention; at the same time, state-owned shareholders should fully play their role in corporate governance, pay attention to the ownership control of invested enterprises, especially whether the actual controller&#39;s behavior conforms to the interests of the enterprise. Based on this, this case study centers around the core knowledge point of &quot;actual controller&quot; and presents the entire process of the control rights battle between Baoneng Group and Huoju Group over JonjeE HI-TECH. On the one hand, it seeks the reasons behind the control rights battle and analyzes the corporate governance problems of JonjeE HI-TECH; on the other hand, by observing the transformation of the ownership control demand of state-owned shareholder Huoju Group, it understands the new requirements of state-owned enterprise reform for state-owned asset governance. Ultimately, it reflects deeply on how enterprises should reshape their corporate governance mechanisms to ensure the effectiveness of internal control and risk management and ensure the stable operation of the enterprise.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">实际控制人；积极股东主义理论；股权分散与公司治理；公司章程与公司治理；国资管控</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
